data.description: Beautiful large first floor two bed, two bath unit with over 1200 square feet of living space, located in a nice area of Harbor City. Features include a large living room and dining room area with a gas fireplace and access to a private balcony, a remodeled kitchen -  complete with granite counter tops and newer stainless steel appliances and a master suite that includes a walk-in closet and a private full bathroom. All this plus a good sized second bedroom and bath, forced air heating and central cooling, inside laundry, roof top deck with community BBQ and two over-sized parking spaces in a gated subterranean garage make this a unit not to be missed. Virtual tour: https://mls.ricohtours.com/4d4804f2-7bb3-4a27-bd92-26868ac4363b
